| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4797 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8756ec77-3b93-5ab9-86f3-cdd32282e49e"
